ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectStony Plain & District Chamber of Commerce, Alberta ** Change Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the STONY PLAIN & DISTRICT CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Alberta, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from the County of Parkland No. 31 and the Town of Stony Plain to the City of Spruce Grove, the Town of Stony Plain, and Parkland County, including the villages of Spring Lake and Wabamun, the summer villages of Seba Beach and Kapasiwin, and the hamlets of Carvel, Duffield, and Fallis, in Alberta.
